data.description:
Imagine your morning coffee on your covered lanai, and a family of deer come to visit.  This is a regular occurrence.
From the front porch with a cozy sitting area to the finished garage, every detail has been thoughtfully considered. LVP flooring graces the living spaces, complemented by neutral paint tones. The care and attention poured into maintaining this home are evident at every turn. The heart of the home is the beautifully appointed kitchen, where modern conveniences meet sleek design. Imagine cooking your favorite meals in your open-concept layout seamlessly connecting the living and dining areas, offering a perfect setting for both everyday moments and entertaining guests. Elegance meets functionality in the primary bedroom, boasting a massive walk-in closet. The split floorplan ensures privacy, with one secondary bedroom featuring an ensuite bath—an ideal retreat for guests or family. This home is not just a residence; it's a haven where memories are made and cherished.
